column3: Specifies that an entity is a party to the context i.e. it has decision making abilities or has obligations and responsibilities
Specifies the human individual or Person involved as the first party
Specifies the entity organisation involved as the second party
Specifies the a party other than the person or Entity that is involved
Specifies the authority that is involved
Specifies the agent that represents a party and can act on behalf
Specifies the party that is responsible for the activity
Specifies the agent that represents a party and can act on behalf of it to make decisions regarding privacy (and related matters)
column9: Privacy Agents can be human or non-human i.e. machine agents
